{"tid":1692252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"豚王集團/我武者羅老闆係我個藍屍老竇嘅藍屍朋友","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T07:09:17.000Z","uid":197813,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f82018c75cc8c08e6eda787e8e2443b5545b89cd","tid":1692252,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"沙田新城市 我武者羅 係藍店 係我個藍屍老竇個藍屍朋友開的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我係呢個post嘅樓主<br />\n<br />\n開頭我有眼不識泰山 唔知嗰個廢老鄧慶治係一個集團嘅非執行董事 以為只係一間舖嘅老闆仔 後來有人話呢間舖係豚王嘅 我去search一search先發現到原來除咗沙田仲有幾間分店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCYiJZp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCYiJZp.jpg&h=8e8861e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話鄧振豪就係鄧慶治個仔 但我唔知可以點fc 不過鄧慶治咁大粒 持有好多股權呢樣嘢就一撚定係事實嚟<br />\n<br />\n分店包括<br />\n中環威靈頓街69號地下<br />\n銅鑼灣登龍街18號V Point地下4號鋪<br />\n太古城太古城道20號元宮閣地下404舖<br />\n尖沙咀加拿分道40-46號香檳大廈地下6號舖<br />\n沙田新城市廣場第一期L1,167號舖<br />\n荃灣大壩街4-30號荃灣廣場1樓115舖<br />\n將軍澳唐賢街9號PopCorn商場地下G25號舖<br />\n「澳門銀河&trade;」地下，G117鋪<br />\n上海市靜安區銅仁路88號L112,L212室<br />\n<br />\n鄧慶治 Mingo 92687268<br />\n舖頭ig <a href=\"https://instagram.com/gamusharahongkong?igshid=t05aau7lkxle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fgamusharahongkong%3Figshid%3Dt05aau7lkxle&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=4fd3b465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/gamusharahongkong?igshid=t05aau7lkxle</a>"},{"pid":"46ff8a67862f9fb53592954bb155963464cb9d15","tid":1692252,"uid":230714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"人性光輝💦"},{"pid":"76223f6d488a44c0dfb0e2128e0b7ea9dc8f1e8a","tid":1692252,"uid":197813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46ff8a67862f9fb53592954bb155963464cb9d15","tid":1692252,"uid":230714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03: